breakid
------------------------------------------
A new symmetry detecting and breaking library. This is based on Jo Devriendt's
BreakID code. It has been re-licensed by the original author to be MIT and
hence it's realeased as MIT here. All modifications by Mate Soos.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libbliss0-0.77-1bl2
  libbreakid-devel-3.1.3-1bl1
  libbreakid3.1-3.1.3-1bl1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libbliss-devel-0.77-1bl2
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/meelgroup/breakid

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/meelgroup/breakid/archive/refs/tags/release/3.1.3.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack breakid-3.1.3-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./breakid-3.1.3-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/breakid-3.1.3-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/breakid-3.1.3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbreakid3.1-3.1.3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbreakid-devel-3.1.3-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(breakid)
  /usr/bin/breakid.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/breakid.README
  /usr/share/doc/breakid/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/breakid/README.md

(libbreakid3.1)
  /usr/bin/cygbreakid-3.1.dll

(libbreakid-devel)
  /usr/include/breakid/breakid.hpp
  /usr/include/breakid/breakid_c.h
  /usr/lib/cmake/breakid/breakidConfig.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/breakid/breakidTargets-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/breakid/breakidTargets.cmake
  /usr/lib/libbreakid.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/breakid.pc

